msgctxt "QL_RiversideMini_CastleWeapon_Desc"
msgid ""
"Though Hyrule Castle was destroyed 100 years\n"
"ago, somewhere inside it still sleeps rare\n"
"equipment from those days. It is famed\n"
"among collectors as the <1.se_co>royal guard's series<2.re_co>.\n"
"Parcy, a traveler at the stable, wants nothing\n"
"more than to see one of them.\n"
"\n"
"However, the castle is a dangerous place\n"
"nowadays, and ordinary folk risk their lives\n"
"getting close..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
